{"tid":1110791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【游泳】何詩蓓獲Big Ten嘉許　密大第3人奪榮譽獎項","createTime":"2019-04-16T16:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T16:44:09.000Z","uid":64751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb8bc586068f997aeae96f6c652b6a6622930ac","tid":1110791,"uid":64751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"何詩蓓再為香港爭光。<br />\n日前於長池游泳錦標賽連奪兩A標殺入東京奧運的何詩蓓（Siobhan），昨日飛回美國隨即獲Big Ten賽會頒發「Medal of Honor」，是密歇根大學歷來泳隊第3人，亦是香港首人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2687802/org/eed3a2bab8012dbcaef5399d59645b92.jpg/ALqHstWsWS5PHRnsFHZAmBibMK7A0hDv8UBty_FAbcs?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2687802%2Forg%2Feed3a2bab8012dbcaef5399d59645b92.jpg%2FALqHstWsWS5PHRnsFHZAmBibMK7A0hDv8UBty_FAbcs%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=3661a185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Medal of Honor」由1951年開頒發，並向運動及學業有卓越表現的準畢業生嘉許。<br />\n周日速速奪得女子100米及200米自由泳東奧A標的何詩蓓，昨日回到美國隨即獲Big Ten賽會頒發此獎項，成為密大第3人獲得此殊榮。<br />\n<br />\n5月將畢業的Siobhan年頭以密大隊長身分於Big Ten贏得總亞軍，並奪下個5金2銀的個人獎項。然而修讀心理學的她成續亦彪炳，因此獲大學提名競逐「Medal of Honor」榮譽。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BETWEEN，呢件咩泳衣黎，咁透嘅，記得唔好買俾條女</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fefcbc37c73e035e25aa00ea057a9b36faa0bcb1","tid":1110791,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"肥左好多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}